"```sql\nSELECT COUNT(DISTINCT drivers.driverId)\nFROM drivers\nJOIN results ON drivers.driverId = results.driverId\nJOIN races ON results.raceId = races.raceId\nWHERE drivers.nationality = 'British'\nAND races.name = 'Australian Grand Prix'\nAND races.year = 2008;\n```\n\nThis SQL query counts the number of distinct drivers with British nationality who participated in the 2008 Australian Grand Prix. It joins the `drivers`, `results`, and `races` tables to filter the data based on the specified conditions."